<PackageManifest Version="2.0.0" xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/developer/vsx-schema/2011" xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/developer/vsx-schema-design/2011"><Metadata><Identity Language="en-US" Id="nooga-portfolio" Publisher="nooga" Version="1.0.141" /><DisplayName>Nooga Portfolio</DisplayName><Description xml:space="preserve">Nooga Portfolio adds portfolio management to Azure DevOps. Connect OKRs to epics, visualise roadmaps, and track strategy execution across teams in real time.</Description><GalleryFlags>Public Paid</GalleryFlags><Properties><Property Id="Microsoft.VisualStudio.Services.GalleryProperties.TrialDays" Value="28" /><Property Id="Microsoft.VisualStudio.Services.Branding.Color" Value="#1a3bc3" /><Property Id="Microsoft.VisualStudio.Services.Branding.Theme" Value="dark" /><Property Id="Microsoft.VisualStudio.Services.Links.Support" Value="mailto:support.portfolio@nooga.net" /><Property Id="Microsoft.VisualStudio.Services.EnableMarketplaceQnA" Value="true" /><Property Id="Microsoft.VisualStudio.Services.CustomerQnALink" Value="https://nooga.feedbear.com/boards/portfolio-feature-requests" /></Properties><Tags>Portfolio management,OKR management,OKR tracking,Enterprise OKRs,Portfolio OKRs,LPM,Lean portfolio management,SAFe,SAFe portfolio management,Agile portfolio management,Enterprise agile,Enterprise agile planning,Strategic planning,Strategy execution,Strategy execution alignment,Epic management,Portfolio roadmap,Roadmap visualization,Portfolio planning,Portfolio governance,Agile governance,PI planning,PI planning portfolio,ART portfolio visibility,Value Management Office,LACE,__BYOLENFORCED</Tags><Categories>Azure Boards</Categories><Icon>static/nooga-symbol-marketplace.png</Icon><License>docs/marketplace/LICENSE.md</License></Metadata><Dependencies /><Installation><InstallationTarget Id="Microsoft.VisualStudio.Services.Cloud" /></Installation><Assets><Asset Type="static/marketplace/Feature-1-Holistic-Overview.png" d:Source="File" Path="sta